action-group.diy-instructions:
Login to your forum as admin, browse to the db_update.php file if it doesnt work for you, you can manually run this in phpmyadmin:
ALTER TABLE phpbb_users ADD user_steam VARCHAR( 255 ) NOT NULL DEFAULT '';
Once run, delete the file, purge the cache, refresh the template, theme and imageset in the ACP. If you want a small steam icon instead on the viewtopic page after install go to contrib/small_icon_on_viewtopic/install_mod.xml or if you want it required by registration go to contrib/required_by_registration/install_mod.xml
